    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Whether for baking, cooking, seasoning, garnishing, meal prep, and more, these glass pinch bowls from Beille will come in handy for just about everything in the kitchen! Also great for snacks, dips, sauces, condiments, or varying accoutrements that might accompany charcuterie boards or other plates and meals. Made from durable glass, the pinch bowls are BPA free and of course, food safe! The condiment cups are easy to maintain and will not warp, stain or absorb previous odors or flavors. These bowls are the perfect size for pre-measuring all kinds of different ingredients, while the clear glass design allows for quick identification of contents. Easy to use and naturally space saving in their design, the ramekins conveniently stack within one another! Measuring just 3</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Beille Cooking Baking Supplies Glass Pinch Bowl Ramekin Kitchen Essentials Set</h2>\n  <p>Whether for baking, cooking, seasoning, garnishing, meal prep, and more, these glass pinch bowls from Beille will come in handy for just about everything in the kitchen! Also great for snacks, dips, sauces, condiments, or varying accoutrements that might accompany charcuterie boards or other plates and meals.</p>\n  <p>Made from durable glass, the pinch bowls are BPA free and of course, food safe! The condiment cups are easy to maintain and will not warp, stain or absorb previous odors or flavors. These bowls are the perfect size for pre-measuring all kinds of different ingredients, while the clear glass design allows for quick identification of contents.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Overall Dimensions: 3.0 wide x 1.5 inch deep; Single Pinch Bowl Weight: 0.2lbs; Material: Glass; Color: Clear</li>\n    <li><strong>3 INCH PINCH BOWLS:</strong> Whether for baking, cooking, garnishing or meal prep, these small glass pinch bowls will come in handy for just about everything! Also great for snacks, dips, sauces, condiments or varying accouterments that might accompany other plates and meals</li>\n    <li><strong>DURABLE GLASS CONDIMENT CUPS:</strong> The pinch bowls are BPA free and food safe; the mini condiment cups are easy to clean and will not warp, stain or absorb existing odors or flavors; these mini kitchen bowls are the perfect size for food and meal prep, while the clear design allows for quick identification of contents</li>\n    <li><strong>STACKABLE SMALL BOWLS:</strong> Easy to use and space saving in design, the pinch bowls conveniently stack within one another; measuring just 3 inches in diameter, these condiment cups will be easy to store and take up minimal space in your kitchen</li>\n    <li><strong>DISHWASHER SAFE BOWLS:</strong> No hand washing needed. Easy to keep clean, these durable glass mini pinch bowls can withstand high temperature heat and are safe for top rack dish washing; freezer and microwave safe as well</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/home/kitchen/47332_mini_ramekins_detail_06.jpg\" alt=\"Whether for baking, cooking, seasoning, garnishing, meal prep, and more, these glass pinch bowls from Beille will come in handy for just about\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> BPNCHBWL225</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058489067</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Clear</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> 3 in</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Easy to use and naturally space saving in their design, the ramekins conveniently stack within one another! Measuring just 3.0 inches in diameter, the condiment cups will be easy to store, and will take up minimal space in kitchen cupboards, drawers or countertops.</p>\n  <p>And last but certainly not least, no handwashing is needed here! Easy to keep clean, these durable glass ramekins can withstand high temperature heat and are safe for top rack dish washing; freezer and microwave safe as well.</p>\n  <p>The glass pinch bowls are also a great arts and crafts item and kids snacks holder too!</p>\n  <p>Available in sets of 4, 8 or 12 units.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "Whether for baking, cooking, seasoning, garnishing, meal prep, and more, these glass pinch bowls from Beille will come in handy for just about everything in the kitchen! Also great for snacks, dips, sauces, condiments, or varying accoutrements that might accompany charcuterie boards or other plates and meals. Made from durable glass, the pinch bowls are BPA free and of course, food safe! The condiment cups are easy to maintain and will not warp, stain or absorb previous odors or flavors. These bowls are the perfect size for pre-measuring all kinds of different ingredients, while the clear glass design allows for quick identification of contents. Easy to use and naturally space saving in their design, the ramekins conveniently stack within one another! Measuring just 3.",
